1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:01:00,000
(Watch on www.dramacool.club Support Admin)

2
00:01:37,890 --> 00:01:41,030
[The Epoch of Miyu]

3
00:01:41,110 --> 00:01:43,920
[Episode 24]

4
00:01:52,070 --> 00:01:53,130
It's for your foot.

5
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:56,800
Thank you.

6
00:01:56,830 --> 00:01:57,880
Let me help.

7
00:01:59,789 --> 00:02:00,680
Lift it up.

8
00:02:01,190 --> 00:02:02,190
[Banquet Hall]

9
00:02:01,950 --> 00:02:02,680
Hold on to me.

10
00:02:16,070 --> 00:02:16,880
Does it hurt?

11
00:02:18,480 --> 00:02:19,280
Bear with it

12
00:02:19,380 --> 00:02:20,470
for a moment.

13
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:40,600
All done.

14
00:02:41,970 --> 00:02:42,850
Thank you.

15
00:02:48,290 --> 00:02:50,810
[Banquet Hall]

16
00:02:49,030 --> 00:02:52,570
Now, let's welcome Ms. Dianjiangchun!

17
00:02:52,640 --> 00:02:53,900
I need to get in there now.

18
00:02:53,900 --> 00:02:54,810
Okay.

19
00:02:55,260 --> 00:02:58,340
[Banquet Hall]

20
00:03:07,500 --> 00:03:11,570
-Dianjiangchun!
-Dianjiangchun!

21
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:10,890
[The Amazing Vlog Producer Dianjiangchun]

22
00:03:34,920 --> 00:03:36,010
Turn up the AC.

23
00:03:36,030 --> 00:03:37,060
There are too many people here.

24
00:03:37,060 --> 00:03:38,100
It's really stuffy.

25
00:03:38,100 --> 00:03:39,300
Thank you all

26
00:03:39,660 --> 00:03:40,880
for coming afar

27
00:03:40,940 --> 00:03:42,680
for me and my book,

28
00:03:40,980 --> 00:03:42,370
[Dianjiangchun
New Book Sharing and Signing Event]

29
00:03:42,700 --> 00:03:44,510
"Chun's Daily Taste."

30
00:03:44,540 --> 00:03:45,550
Thank you.

31
00:03:51,710 --> 00:03:52,560
Xu Miyu!

32
00:03:53,770 --> 00:03:54,420
Mr. Duan.

33
00:03:55,010 --> 00:03:56,630
I was wondering
why I couldn't get a helper.

34
00:03:56,630 --> 00:03:58,230
It's quite boisterous here.

35
00:03:58,400 --> 00:04:00,370
Mr. Duan, I'll get you a helper
if you need one.

36
00:04:00,370 --> 00:04:01,090
Well,

37
00:04:01,110 --> 00:04:03,430
five or six people will come meet me soon.

38
00:04:03,460 --> 00:04:04,990
I need you to lead them to me.

39
00:04:05,010 --> 00:04:06,090
Sorry, Mr. Duan.

40
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:07,680
I'm afraid I'm tied up here.

41
00:04:07,700 --> 00:04:08,930
To make sure the meetup goes well,

42
00:04:08,930 --> 00:04:10,950
how about I ask someone else
to receive them for you?

43
00:04:10,950 --> 00:04:11,660
Xu Miyu,

44
00:04:12,030 --> 00:04:12,960
what do you mean?

45
00:04:13,270 --> 00:04:14,360
Are my friends not worthy

46
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:16,820
of being received
by you, the lobby manager?

47
00:04:17,010 --> 00:04:18,709
That's not what I mean, Mr. Duan.

48
00:04:18,709 --> 00:04:19,269
I...

49
00:04:21,010 --> 00:04:22,270
May I have

50
00:04:22,270 --> 00:04:24,070
your friends' photos and names?

51
00:04:24,890 --> 00:04:26,350
Ask my assistant for them.

52
00:04:32,900 --> 00:04:33,820
Lu Xiaoyan.

53
00:04:36,630 --> 00:04:38,980
There's a task for you.
It's about the book signing event.

54
00:04:38,980 --> 00:04:39,860
What is it?

55
00:04:39,880 --> 00:04:40,680
I've sent it to you.

56
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:42,140
Check it out on your phone.

57
00:04:44,870 --> 00:04:46,200
Hello, enjoy your stay.

58
00:04:54,580 --> 00:04:56,240
It's way too blurry, isn't it?

59
00:04:56,740 --> 00:04:57,600
Mr. Ma Wenhui

60
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:59,240
is an important guest
for the upcoming talk.

61
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:00,720
It's been a long time
since he last attended a public event.

62
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:01,510
This is the clearest photo

63
00:05:01,510 --> 00:05:03,370
of his that could be found online.

64
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:04,160
But don't worry.

65
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:05,940
He'll come to you when he arrives.

66
00:05:05,940 --> 00:05:08,140
Your task is to bring him to the venue.

67
00:05:08,250 --> 00:05:09,010
Got it.

68
00:05:09,200 --> 00:05:10,740
I obtained some information about him

69
00:05:10,740 --> 00:05:11,560
from the internet.

70
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:12,310
Why don't I send it to you?

71
00:05:12,310 --> 00:05:13,240
No need.

72
00:05:13,660 --> 00:05:15,090
You should do some research online
as well.

73
00:05:15,090 --> 00:05:17,070
He's a complete stranger to us after all.

74
00:05:17,070 --> 00:05:18,280
Better safe than sorry.

75
00:05:18,280 --> 00:05:19,340
How do I have time for that?

76
00:05:19,340 --> 00:05:20,070
I'm just an usher.

77
00:05:20,070 --> 00:05:22,170
Am I even supposed to memorize
the guest's background?

78
00:05:22,170 --> 00:05:25,070
If you're concerned,
assign the task to someone else.

79
00:05:25,070 --> 00:05:25,910
Hello.

80
00:05:26,090 --> 00:05:27,050
I can see here

81
00:05:27,070 --> 00:05:29,800
that you booked a deluxe king room.
Is it correct?

82
00:05:31,560 --> 00:05:33,690
Why does she have to be so hoity-toity?

83
00:05:44,100 --> 00:05:46,010
Hello, I'm the lobby manager
of Purong Hotel.

84
00:05:46,010 --> 00:05:46,720
This way, please.

85
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:47,350
Okay.

86
00:05:52,640 --> 00:05:53,640
Have you noticed?

87
00:05:54,600 --> 00:05:55,430
Ms. Xu has rushed

88
00:05:55,430 --> 00:05:57,320
in and out several times today.

89
00:05:57,350 --> 00:05:58,350
Serves her right.

90
00:05:58,570 --> 00:06:00,130
She loves to show off, doesn't she?

91
00:06:00,130 --> 00:06:01,400
Now she can do it all day long.

92
00:06:01,400 --> 00:06:03,460
I just hope she can stay out of my hair.

93
00:06:04,700 --> 00:06:05,580
Next, please!

94
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:07,560
Hello.

95
00:06:07,580 --> 00:06:08,680
Your ID, please.

96
00:06:10,350 --> 00:06:11,470
Where's my bag?

97
00:06:12,600 --> 00:06:13,610
Next!

98
00:06:13,970 --> 00:06:14,770
Hold on, miss.

99
00:06:15,350 --> 00:06:17,440
I left my bag in the taxi.

100
00:06:17,460 --> 00:06:19,060
All my personal documents are in it.

101
00:06:19,060 --> 00:06:20,420
Could you make an exception?

102
00:06:20,420 --> 00:06:22,400
I'm here for the talk
in the book signing event.

103
00:06:22,400 --> 00:06:23,720
Sorry, sir.

104
00:06:24,060 --> 00:06:26,670
There are over 100 attendees
of this event.

105
00:06:26,830 --> 00:06:28,830
I need to verify your identity.

106
00:06:29,340 --> 00:06:30,900
I advise you to call

107
00:06:30,950 --> 00:06:32,750
the taxi company right now

108
00:06:32,750 --> 00:06:33,750
to retrieve you bag.

109
00:06:33,750 --> 00:06:35,630
You won't be admitted to the venue
without a valid ID.

110
00:06:35,630 --> 00:06:37,720
But the talk is about to start.

111
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:39,830
Sorry, sir. There's nothing I can do.

112
00:06:40,080 --> 00:06:40,890
Ma'am.

113
00:06:47,750 --> 00:06:49,270
Sir, smoking is prohibited here.

114
00:06:49,270 --> 00:06:51,670
If you are to smoke,
could you step outside?

115
00:06:56,510 --> 00:06:57,310
Cleaning staff,

116
00:06:57,310 --> 00:06:59,310
the reception area needs cleaning.

117
00:07:01,450 --> 00:07:02,870
What am I supposed to do?

118
00:07:03,190 --> 00:07:04,830
Well, this is...

119
00:07:06,370 --> 00:07:08,170
Anything wrong? What happened?

120
00:07:08,310 --> 00:07:10,770
Mr. Ji, we can't reach
the guest speaker now.

121
00:07:10,870 --> 00:07:12,310
Ms. Xu is handling it.

122
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:14,270
Ms. Xu.

123
00:07:14,270 --> 00:07:14,750
Mr. Ji.

124
00:07:15,020 --> 00:07:16,300
I'll go with you to look for the guest.

125
00:07:16,300 --> 00:07:17,150
Okay.

126
00:07:17,170 --> 00:07:17,970
Ji Feng!

127
00:07:20,030 --> 00:07:20,830
Ji Feng,

128
00:07:21,150 --> 00:07:23,010
the talk will begin in 10 minutes.

129
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:24,960
Can you stick around and help me?

130
00:07:25,550 --> 00:07:27,690
Mr. Ji, maybe you should stay
and assist Ms. Jiang.

131
00:07:27,690 --> 00:07:29,620
I can go look for the guest on my own.

132
00:07:29,830 --> 00:07:30,690
Are you sure...

133
00:07:31,330 --> 00:07:32,170
you can do it alone?

134
00:07:32,170 --> 00:07:33,090
Yes.

135
00:07:33,190 --> 00:07:35,140
Okay. Call me anytime
if there's a problem.

136
00:07:35,140 --> 00:07:36,090
I'll be off then.

137
00:07:38,159 --> 00:07:38,600
Come with me.

138
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:39,040
Okay.

139
00:07:44,360 --> 00:07:45,870
Did you receive

140
00:07:45,900 --> 00:07:47,760
a middle-aged man with gray hair?

141
00:07:54,390 --> 00:07:55,190
Lu Xiaoyan,

142
00:07:55,210 --> 00:07:56,340
did you receive him?

143
00:07:58,060 --> 00:07:59,150
Where has he gone?

144
00:07:59,990 --> 00:08:01,790
H-He's gone for a smoke outside.

145
00:08:23,910 --> 00:08:24,510
Hello,

146
00:08:24,510 --> 00:08:26,160
hailing service?

147
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:30,870
Up next is a discussion.

148
00:08:31,120 --> 00:08:32,840
Let's welcome Ms. Dianjiangchun

149
00:08:32,840 --> 00:08:35,080
with a round of applause!

150
00:08:35,110 --> 00:08:36,820
-Hurray!
-Hurray!

151
00:08:39,320 --> 00:08:40,250
Dianjiangchun!

152
00:08:42,630 --> 00:08:43,539
Dianjiangchun!

153
00:08:43,539 --> 00:08:44,400
[Always on the road
recording the flavors of the mortal world]

154
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:46,960
Hello, everyone.

155
00:08:47,390 --> 00:08:48,750
Today's talk

156
00:08:48,750 --> 00:08:50,650
was supposed to be held
between me

157
00:08:50,690 --> 00:08:52,530
and my mentor, Mr. Ma Wenhui.

158
00:08:52,560 --> 00:08:54,870
But unfortunately,
due to unexpected circumstances,

159
00:08:54,870 --> 00:08:57,200
Mr. Ma couldn't make it here today.

160
00:08:58,020 --> 00:08:59,100
Nonetheless,

161
00:08:59,120 --> 00:09:01,120
I'm honored to have invited

162
00:09:01,150 --> 00:09:03,030
a good friend of mine to the talk.

163
00:09:03,070 --> 00:09:04,870
He's the general manager of this hotel,

164
00:09:04,870 --> 00:09:07,930
who rose to fame online
for his saxophone performance.

165
00:09:11,510 --> 00:09:13,620
Ji Feng, come up on the stage.

166
00:09:14,630 --> 00:09:17,320
-Nice!
-Great!

167
00:09:26,730 --> 00:09:29,860
First, thank you all
for not turning around and leaving.

168
00:09:32,390 --> 00:09:33,960
Let me briefly introduce myself.

169
00:09:33,960 --> 00:09:36,710
I'm Ji Feng,
the general manager of Purong Hotel.

170
00:09:36,740 --> 00:09:39,100
I believe the essence of today's talk

171
00:09:39,120 --> 00:09:41,480
isn't the topic itself,
but your very presence.

172
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:43,270
You showing up here is already meaningful.

173
00:09:43,270 --> 00:09:45,150
It's just like a sentence in the book:

174
00:09:45,150 --> 00:09:47,000
"Every meeting is a long-awaited reunion."

175
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:48,340
I'd like to interview Ms. Dianjiangchun.

176
00:09:48,340 --> 00:09:50,700
Is there a story behind this sentence?

177
00:09:52,930 --> 00:09:56,590
Mr. Ji is fishing for gossip
right after getting on the stage, huh?

178
00:10:16,080 --> 00:10:21,010
[Nanxun Road]

179
00:10:21,470 --> 00:10:22,280
Hello,

180
00:10:22,320 --> 00:10:24,020
hailing service, right?

181
00:10:26,210 --> 00:10:27,210
You found the bag?

182
00:10:30,210 --> 00:10:31,600
Could you have it delivered

183
00:10:31,600 --> 00:10:33,080
to the lobby of Purong Hotel?

184
00:10:33,080 --> 00:10:34,050
I'll be there.

185
00:10:37,580 --> 00:10:40,880
Mr. Ma said he'd like to pick it up
somewhere else?

186
00:10:42,120 --> 00:10:42,920
Okay.

187
00:10:42,940 --> 00:10:44,220
I got it. Thanks.

188
00:11:13,020 --> 00:11:15,560
[Dianjiangchun
New Book Sharing and Signing Event]

189
00:11:19,280 --> 00:11:21,700
May I ask a personal question?

190
00:11:21,720 --> 00:11:23,890
Are the two of you dating?

191
00:11:24,710 --> 00:11:27,080
You two really make a perfect couple!

192
00:11:25,890 --> 00:11:27,350
[Dianjiangchun
New Book Sharing and Signing Event]

193
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:29,310
Hailin,

194
00:11:29,330 --> 00:11:30,520
I'm terribly sorry.

195
00:11:30,540 --> 00:11:33,060
Mr. Ma won't be back to the hotel.

196
00:11:33,130 --> 00:11:33,800
It's okay.

197
00:11:33,830 --> 00:11:35,680
We already have a guest for the talk.

198
00:11:35,680 --> 00:11:37,600
They're dropping juicy gossip now.

199
00:11:37,600 --> 00:11:39,600
I treasure each and every one of you.

200
00:11:39,790 --> 00:11:40,650
So,

201
00:11:41,080 --> 00:11:42,480
I don't want to lie to you.

202
00:11:44,190 --> 00:11:45,090
The two of us...

203
00:11:46,480 --> 00:11:47,480
used to be in love.

204
00:11:57,170 --> 00:11:57,840
Have you two

205
00:11:57,840 --> 00:12:00,910
considered getting back together?

206
00:12:00,910 --> 00:12:03,570
Yes! Yeah!

207
00:12:03,600 --> 00:12:04,650
To me...

208
00:12:05,320 --> 00:12:07,200
Mr. Ji is a great work partner.

209
00:12:07,350 --> 00:12:10,580
Among all the people
I've collaborated with,

210
00:12:10,600 --> 00:12:13,790
I deem Mr. Ji as
the most trustworthy and compatible one.

211
00:12:14,040 --> 00:12:15,860
As for the future,

212
00:12:16,720 --> 00:12:17,920
I'll leave it to fate.

213
00:12:23,440 --> 00:12:25,460
Just as expected of Dianjiangchun.

214
00:12:26,470 --> 00:12:28,010
Look at the audience's reaction.

215
00:12:28,010 --> 00:12:29,940
These fans have definitely
got their value out of coming here,

216
00:12:29,940 --> 00:12:32,290
as they could witness
something so romantic.

217
00:12:32,290 --> 00:12:34,130
Ms. Xu, look!

218
00:12:36,890 --> 00:12:39,250
Mr. Ji, have you met Ms. Jiang before?

219
00:12:39,270 --> 00:12:40,270
She and I...

220
00:12:41,940 --> 00:12:43,400
went to college together.

221
00:13:05,710 --> 00:13:13,750
[Purong Hotel]

222
00:13:13,980 --> 00:13:14,810
Lu Xiaoyan,

223
00:13:15,510 --> 00:13:16,440
I need you to write

224
00:13:16,440 --> 00:13:18,300
a report about today's incident.

225
00:13:18,900 --> 00:13:20,020
What incident?

226
00:13:20,220 --> 00:13:21,720
What's there to write about?

227
00:13:21,720 --> 00:13:23,330
I demand a detailed explanation.

228
00:13:23,330 --> 00:13:23,970
First,

229
00:13:24,000 --> 00:13:25,080
what was your attitude like

230
00:13:25,080 --> 00:13:26,750
when you received Mr. Ma Wenhui?

231
00:13:26,750 --> 00:13:27,280
Second,

232
00:13:27,320 --> 00:13:28,550
why did he never come back

233
00:13:28,550 --> 00:13:30,080
after going out for a smoke?

234
00:13:35,350 --> 00:13:36,440
I've reported

235
00:13:36,440 --> 00:13:38,460
to Director Bai about what happened.

236
00:13:38,460 --> 00:13:39,960
You can go ask him for more details.

237
00:13:39,960 --> 00:13:41,020
I am asking you now.

238
00:13:42,240 --> 00:13:43,670
How could you drive away a guest

239
00:13:43,670 --> 00:13:45,000
who came to you for help?

240
00:13:45,320 --> 00:13:47,360
I-I didn't drive him away, did I?

241
00:13:47,360 --> 00:13:49,480
I was just following the hotel's protocol.

242
00:13:49,480 --> 00:13:50,720
ID verification

243
00:13:50,720 --> 00:13:51,910
and the no-smoking policy

244
00:13:51,910 --> 00:13:54,120
are clearly stated
in the hotel regulations.

245
00:13:54,120 --> 00:13:55,250
Attitude determines results.

246
00:13:55,250 --> 00:13:56,440
What kind of attitude did you take

247
00:13:56,440 --> 00:13:58,240
when enforcing hotel policies?

248
00:13:58,580 --> 00:13:59,840
The hotel also requires you

249
00:13:59,840 --> 00:14:00,910
to do everything possible

250
00:14:00,910 --> 00:14:02,690
to help guests solve their problems.

251
00:14:02,690 --> 00:14:04,890
Did you help Mr. Ma look for his lost bag?

252
00:14:05,710 --> 00:14:06,860
I was swamped just now.

253
00:14:06,860 --> 00:14:07,480
How was it possible

254
00:14:07,480 --> 00:14:09,200
for me to help a guest
look for a lost item?

255
00:14:09,200 --> 00:14:10,730
Being busy is not an excuse.

256
00:14:10,790 --> 00:14:11,480
Our hotel

257
00:14:11,480 --> 00:14:13,240
accommodates
a large number of guests every day.

258
00:14:13,240 --> 00:14:15,080
You can't treat anyone poorly

259
00:14:15,080 --> 00:14:16,920
just because you're busy.

260
00:14:16,950 --> 00:14:18,510
Today, you made this mistake

261
00:14:18,510 --> 00:14:19,440
exactly because

262
00:14:19,440 --> 00:14:21,620
you didn't take the task I gave you
seriously.

263
00:14:21,620 --> 00:14:22,840
Let me say this to you again:

264
00:14:22,840 --> 00:14:23,840
whether you like it or not,

265
00:14:23,840 --> 00:14:24,790
I am the lobby manager

266
00:14:24,790 --> 00:14:25,960
and your supervisor now,

267
00:14:25,960 --> 00:14:26,720
which means you must

268
00:14:26,720 --> 00:14:28,520
complete the tasks I assign you.

269
00:14:31,480 --> 00:14:32,320
Lastly,

270
00:14:32,570 --> 00:14:34,280
do you know how important

271
00:14:34,320 --> 00:14:36,420
this book signing event is to our hotel?

272
00:14:36,420 --> 00:14:38,360
The entire event could've been ruined

273
00:14:38,360 --> 00:14:39,910
due to a small slip you made.

274
00:14:40,030 --> 00:14:42,230
Could you have borne the consequences?

275
00:14:43,240 --> 00:14:45,200
Isn't the talk going well now?

276
00:14:45,200 --> 00:14:47,860
That's because
someone is fixing your mistake.

277
00:14:48,700 --> 00:14:50,060
Tomorrow morning,

278
00:14:50,090 --> 00:14:52,090
submit a written explanation to me.

279
00:14:52,340 --> 00:14:53,990
Ten points will be deducted
from your performance rating this month.

280
00:14:53,990 --> 00:14:55,150
Take it as a lesson.

281
00:14:55,450 --> 00:14:57,810
What? A 10-point deduction?

282
00:14:57,870 --> 00:14:59,330
I didn't mean to offend him.

283
00:14:59,330 --> 00:15:00,240
I really didn't know

284
00:15:00,240 --> 00:15:02,000
he was the guest speaker.

285
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:02,950
If I had known,

286
00:15:02,980 --> 00:15:04,840
I would've treated him properly.

287
00:15:05,600 --> 00:15:06,570
Miyu!

288
00:15:07,040 --> 00:15:07,860
That's my sister,

289
00:15:07,860 --> 00:15:09,200
the lobby manager.

290
00:15:09,790 --> 00:15:10,790
Anyway,

291
00:15:10,790 --> 00:15:13,450
you must take responsibility
for your mistake.

292
00:15:15,210 --> 00:15:16,010
Miyao.

293
00:15:17,520 --> 00:15:18,640
It's a real delight

294
00:15:18,720 --> 00:15:20,790
to have gathered with you today

295
00:15:20,790 --> 00:15:22,320
and had such a fantastic talk.

296
00:15:22,320 --> 00:15:23,840
In the days ahead,

297
00:15:23,840 --> 00:15:26,050
no matter how busy or anxious

298
00:15:26,070 --> 00:15:27,280
you may be,

299
00:15:27,360 --> 00:15:28,790
I hope

300
00:15:28,790 --> 00:15:31,120
all of you can find your inner peace

301
00:15:31,120 --> 00:15:33,840
in your stressful everyday lives.

302
00:15:34,360 --> 00:15:37,960
I'd appreciate it if you could continue
supporting me and staying connected

303
00:15:37,960 --> 00:15:38,960
with me.

304
00:15:42,840 --> 00:15:44,120
Thank you, everyone.

305
00:15:45,630 --> 00:15:46,950
Dianjiangchun!

306
00:15:46,980 --> 00:15:48,380
Dianjiangchun!

307
00:15:48,400 --> 00:15:50,000
Dianjiangchun!

308
00:15:50,020 --> 00:15:51,530
Dianjiangchun!

309
00:15:55,360 --> 00:15:56,270
Sorry.

310
00:15:56,360 --> 00:15:58,240
I let out our secret without your consent.

311
00:15:58,240 --> 00:15:59,320
You're not mad at me, are you?

312
00:15:59,320 --> 00:16:00,080
Not at all.

313
00:16:00,550 --> 00:16:02,730
Our hotel has benefited from this event.

314
00:16:02,730 --> 00:16:04,460
For that, I owe you many thanks.

315
00:16:04,630 --> 00:16:06,820
By the way,
are there extra copies of your book?

316
00:16:06,820 --> 00:16:07,700
Why do you ask?

317
00:16:09,120 --> 00:16:11,740
All our staff are your fans now.

318
00:16:11,760 --> 00:16:13,100
I might as well take this chance

319
00:16:13,100 --> 00:16:14,030
to buy 500 copies

320
00:16:14,200 --> 00:16:15,560
for them as staff perks.

321
00:16:15,860 --> 00:16:17,540
What a pleasure for me, Mr. Ji.

322
00:16:17,840 --> 00:16:19,040
The pleasure is ours.

323
00:16:20,650 --> 00:16:22,270
Thank you, Zhichun.

324
00:16:22,840 --> 00:16:23,720
For what?

325
00:16:25,130 --> 00:16:27,460
For being supportive of Purong Hotel.

326
00:16:29,570 --> 00:16:31,300
Nothing gets past you, does it?

327
00:16:35,950 --> 00:16:37,430
How magnificent.

328
00:16:39,600 --> 00:16:40,860
This is really pretty.

329
00:16:43,320 --> 00:16:45,100
What? I won't break it.

330
00:16:45,600 --> 00:16:46,990
There's even a piano!

331
00:16:47,030 --> 00:16:48,040
Get back out.

332
00:16:48,910 --> 00:16:49,810
No entry.

333
00:16:49,830 --> 00:16:52,070
That's a display for everyone, isn't it?

334
00:16:52,070 --> 00:16:52,910
Let's go.

335
00:16:53,060 --> 00:16:53,790
Honestly,

336
00:16:53,790 --> 00:16:55,180
you look quite smart

337
00:16:55,210 --> 00:16:56,840
in this uniform.

338
00:16:56,860 --> 00:16:58,190
Is anyone pursuing you?

339
00:16:58,380 --> 00:16:59,270
Five-star hotel guests

340
00:16:58,490 --> 00:17:02,160
[Purong Hotel]

341
00:16:59,290 --> 00:17:00,950
all have deep pockets, right?

342
00:17:00,950 --> 00:17:03,150
Quickly find a decent one and marry him.

343
00:17:06,140 --> 00:17:06,970
Thanks.

344
00:17:09,349 --> 00:17:10,280
Miyao,

345
00:17:10,829 --> 00:17:11,920
what on earth brings you here?

346
00:17:11,920 --> 00:17:13,369
A certain matter, of course.

347
00:17:13,369 --> 00:17:14,609
Can we eat and talk

348
00:17:14,640 --> 00:17:16,089
somewhere?

349
00:17:17,030 --> 00:17:18,760
How about the executive lounge

350
00:17:18,780 --> 00:17:20,240
you brought Mom and Dad to last time?

351
00:17:20,240 --> 00:17:22,099
Why not treat me to that place too?

352
00:17:22,109 --> 00:17:23,589
I can't go to the HSKP Department
without cause,

353
00:17:23,589 --> 00:17:25,190
since I work in the lobby now.

354
00:17:25,480 --> 00:17:26,270
I'll be off work soon.

355
00:17:26,270 --> 00:17:28,109
Let me get changed
and take you out for a bite, okay?

356
00:17:28,109 --> 00:17:28,920
Out for a bite?

357
00:17:28,920 --> 00:17:30,250
What do you mean by that?

358
00:17:30,610 --> 00:17:32,220
Are you chasing me away
right after I arrived?

359
00:17:32,220 --> 00:17:33,790
Am I embarrassing you or what?

360
00:17:33,790 --> 00:17:34,790
No, that's not it.

361
00:17:34,810 --> 00:17:35,830
Then what's the reason?

362
00:17:35,830 --> 00:17:36,590
Anyway,

363
00:17:36,650 --> 00:17:38,310
I insist on eating here today.

364
00:17:38,710 --> 00:17:39,940
[Purong Hotel]

365
00:17:41,210 --> 00:17:42,190
Hello, sir.

366
00:17:42,250 --> 00:17:43,580
How may I help you?

367
00:17:43,620 --> 00:17:44,710
I booked a room. Thanks.

368
00:17:44,710 --> 00:17:45,910
Please wait a moment.

369
00:17:46,510 --> 00:17:47,440
Today is no good.

370
00:17:47,820 --> 00:17:50,270
There's an important event
in our hotel today.

371
00:17:50,270 --> 00:17:52,050
I promise I'll take you to the lounge
next time you're here.

372
00:17:52,050 --> 00:17:52,960
Next time?

373
00:17:53,520 --> 00:17:55,310
That means I have to wait then, right?

374
00:17:55,310 --> 00:17:56,070
All I have done

375
00:17:56,070 --> 00:17:57,550
is wait, wait, and wait.

376
00:17:57,810 --> 00:18:00,770
When you were divorced
and busy looking for a job,

377
00:18:00,800 --> 00:18:01,720
I kindly spared you

378
00:18:01,720 --> 00:18:02,960
from trouble out of pity.

379
00:18:02,960 --> 00:18:04,800
Are you saying I have to make
an appointment for a chat

380
00:18:04,800 --> 00:18:07,000
now that you've got your life together?

381
00:18:07,160 --> 00:18:08,570
I don't mean any of that.

382
00:18:10,320 --> 00:18:11,560
Just cut the chase.

383
00:18:12,700 --> 00:18:14,180
What do you want this time?

384
00:18:14,210 --> 00:18:16,650
What do you mean, "what I want this time"?

385
00:18:17,100 --> 00:18:18,580
I'm your sister.

386
00:18:18,850 --> 00:18:21,080
It's not like I'm here to rob you.

387
00:18:21,390 --> 00:18:23,340
I'm actually here to beg you.

388
00:18:23,360 --> 00:18:24,980
I'm begging you

389
00:18:25,080 --> 00:18:26,370
to help your nephew,

390
00:18:26,400 --> 00:18:28,610
given that the entire family supported you

391
00:18:28,610 --> 00:18:30,210
through college in the past.

392
00:18:30,210 --> 00:18:30,960
Will you chip in

393
00:18:30,960 --> 00:18:33,450
to pay for
my son's international school tuition?

394
00:18:33,450 --> 00:18:34,140
Sister,

395
00:18:34,580 --> 00:18:36,190
part of my monthly salary

396
00:18:36,320 --> 00:18:38,080
is spent on Mom and Dad's loans.

397
00:18:38,370 --> 00:18:39,630
I'm unable to help you.

398
00:18:43,570 --> 00:18:45,900
You're indeed different now from before.

399
00:18:46,070 --> 00:18:47,060
Xu Miyu,

400
00:18:47,590 --> 00:18:50,510
what a powerful lobby manager you are now.

401
00:18:50,540 --> 00:18:52,780
Since when have you become  so heartless

402
00:18:52,800 --> 00:18:54,110
and cold to your family?

403
00:18:54,110 --> 00:18:56,110
You're living the high life

404
00:18:56,110 --> 00:18:57,640
in a five-star hotel,

405
00:18:57,670 --> 00:19:00,090
yet you won't lend money
to a family member in need.

406
00:19:00,090 --> 00:19:01,780
Don't you have a conscience?

407
00:19:07,470 --> 00:19:08,360
Miyao,

408
00:19:09,280 --> 00:19:10,240
I, Xu Miyu,

409
00:19:10,950 --> 00:19:11,880
can look you,

410
00:19:12,810 --> 00:19:13,550
Dad, Mom,

411
00:19:14,030 --> 00:19:15,030
and everyone else

412
00:19:15,170 --> 00:19:16,860
in the family that raised me in the eye

413
00:19:16,860 --> 00:19:18,720
and say I have a clear conscience.

414
00:19:19,440 --> 00:19:20,200
I've devoted

415
00:19:20,200 --> 00:19:22,200
everything I have to all of you.

416
00:19:23,270 --> 00:19:25,030
The rest of my life belongs to myself.

417
00:19:25,030 --> 00:19:26,890
I hope you'll stop disturbing me!

418
00:19:27,090 --> 00:19:27,850
Besides,

419
00:19:28,840 --> 00:19:30,280
this is where I work.

420
00:19:31,000 --> 00:19:32,600
You'd better be respectful.

421
00:19:34,000 --> 00:19:34,880
Hello, sir.

422
00:19:34,900 --> 00:19:36,200
Here's your key card and passport.

423
00:19:36,200 --> 00:19:36,750
Please keep them safe.

424
00:19:36,750 --> 00:19:37,680
Okay, thanks.

425
00:19:38,480 --> 00:19:39,680
Have a temper now,

426
00:19:39,680 --> 00:19:41,550
don't you?

427
00:19:41,850 --> 00:19:43,090
I need to go now.

428
00:19:43,330 --> 00:19:44,110
You're not going anywhere!

429
00:19:44,110 --> 00:19:44,970
Listen to me...

430
00:19:45,200 --> 00:19:46,350
What do you mean by this?

431
00:19:46,350 --> 00:19:47,530
You're not going anywhere!

432
00:19:47,530 --> 00:19:49,030
Where are you going, Xu Miyu?

433
00:19:49,030 --> 00:19:50,030
I won't let you go!

434
00:19:52,000 --> 00:19:52,790
Xu Miyu!

435
00:20:03,190 --> 00:20:04,190
Excuse me.

436
00:20:04,280 --> 00:20:05,200
I just got off the plane.

437
00:20:05,200 --> 00:20:06,330
I haven't eaten yet.

438
00:20:06,400 --> 00:20:08,180
Would you go to dinner with me?

439
00:20:35,960 --> 00:20:36,680
Excuse me.

440
00:20:36,680 --> 00:20:38,630
Please have my luggage stored. Thanks.

441
00:20:38,630 --> 00:20:39,490
Let's go.

442
00:20:45,880 --> 00:20:46,710
Is

443
00:20:46,740 --> 00:20:47,670
Mr. Tan...

444
00:20:48,380 --> 00:20:49,140
Yes.

445
00:20:50,730 --> 00:20:51,590
But not really.

446
00:20:54,850 --> 00:20:55,890
Who's that guy?

447
00:20:55,910 --> 00:20:57,280
Is he rich?

448
00:20:57,310 --> 00:21:00,020
Do let me know
when Mr. Ma gets his phone back.

449
00:21:00,240 --> 00:21:02,790
I must formally apologize to him
on behalf of the hotel.

450
00:21:02,790 --> 00:21:03,270
Sure.

451
00:21:03,270 --> 00:21:04,350
I'll arrange it for you.

452
00:21:04,350 --> 00:21:04,960
Okay.

453
00:21:33,420 --> 00:21:34,820
Is that Ms. Xu?

454
00:21:40,370 --> 00:21:42,170
I'll walk you to the parking lot.

455
00:21:42,540 --> 00:21:43,300
Let's go.

456
00:22:01,010 --> 00:22:02,330
Is that Ms. Xu?

457
00:22:09,250 --> 00:22:10,120
Ms. Jiang.

458
00:22:13,260 --> 00:22:13,960
Ms. Jiang?

459
00:22:15,340 --> 00:22:16,510
Photos from the talk are out.

460
00:22:16,510 --> 00:22:17,720
Take a look.

461
00:22:28,150 --> 00:22:29,350
Thanks for the hard work, Jiao.

462
00:22:29,350 --> 00:22:31,550
No problem, Ms. Jiang. I just did my job.

463
00:23:01,320 --> 00:23:02,850
Such tasty wine.

464
00:23:03,170 --> 00:23:04,370
Can I have some more?

465
00:23:14,170 --> 00:23:14,930
Thanks.

466
00:23:17,730 --> 00:23:18,660
Mr. Tan,

467
00:23:19,000 --> 00:23:19,830
thank you.

468
00:23:20,620 --> 00:23:21,550
Look what a spread,

469
00:23:21,550 --> 00:23:24,040
accompanied by nice wine
and beautiful views.

470
00:23:24,040 --> 00:23:26,310
It's been a long, long time

471
00:23:26,880 --> 00:23:28,050
since I had so much joy.

472
00:23:28,050 --> 00:23:28,850
Thank you.

473
00:23:30,350 --> 00:23:31,440
Easy with the wine.

474
00:23:31,460 --> 00:23:32,380
Have more food.

475
00:23:47,240 --> 00:23:48,030
Thanks.

476
00:23:48,350 --> 00:23:49,240
Not too much.

477
00:23:49,590 --> 00:23:50,740
Don't worry.

478
00:23:51,510 --> 00:23:53,750
I'm especially happy today.

479
00:23:53,880 --> 00:23:55,490
It took me so long to finally realize

480
00:23:55,490 --> 00:23:56,170
that saying no

481
00:23:56,170 --> 00:23:57,930
feels so liberating.

482
00:23:58,740 --> 00:24:00,350
Today, I said no to my sister.

483
00:24:01,150 --> 00:24:03,150
I also said no to a colleague of mine.

484
00:24:03,840 --> 00:24:06,410
I had such a wonderful day.

485
00:24:06,680 --> 00:24:07,570
Great.

486
00:24:07,870 --> 00:24:09,000
Congratulations

487
00:24:09,020 --> 00:24:11,750
on starting a life free of constraints.

488
00:24:12,100 --> 00:24:12,930
Cheers.

489
00:24:25,160 --> 00:24:25,920
Give it to me.

490
00:24:32,240 --> 00:24:33,480
When I was little,

491
00:24:34,150 --> 00:24:36,250
I listened to my sister on everything.

492
00:24:36,250 --> 00:24:38,210
I hardly dared to contradict her

493
00:24:38,540 --> 00:24:40,540
or go against her.

494
00:24:41,020 --> 00:24:43,260
She was always the first one to enjoy

495
00:24:43,280 --> 00:24:44,740
all the nice stuff at home.

496
00:24:45,200 --> 00:24:47,240
She got the first bite of delicious food.

497
00:24:47,240 --> 00:24:48,960
She got to wear cute outfits first.

498
00:24:48,960 --> 00:24:49,960
I couldn't have any of those

499
00:24:49,960 --> 00:24:51,490
until she got tired of them.

500
00:24:51,640 --> 00:24:53,370
I even had to say thank you to her

501
00:24:53,900 --> 00:24:55,690
and my parents

502
00:24:56,640 --> 00:24:57,570
just because...

503
00:24:58,270 --> 00:24:59,440
I dared not say no

504
00:24:59,720 --> 00:25:00,880
or refuse.

505
00:25:01,680 --> 00:25:02,880
After I grew up,

506
00:25:03,170 --> 00:25:04,500
they asked me for money.

507
00:25:05,510 --> 00:25:06,550
My sister...

508
00:25:09,160 --> 00:25:11,000
asked me to get her husband a job.

509
00:25:11,610 --> 00:25:14,070
Whatever difficulties I was going through,

510
00:25:14,110 --> 00:25:16,110
I would always satisfy her demands.

511
00:25:16,870 --> 00:25:18,120
But today,

512
00:25:19,830 --> 00:25:21,830
when she came and asked me for money,

513
00:25:22,680 --> 00:25:23,820
I said no.

514
00:25:24,630 --> 00:25:25,760
I told her

515
00:25:26,370 --> 00:25:28,370
that the old Xu Miyu who always tried

516
00:25:28,550 --> 00:25:31,150
to please and pander to others
was already dead

517
00:25:31,200 --> 00:25:31,930
and gone.

518
00:25:32,920 --> 00:25:34,890
Now, I'm a free spirit

519
00:25:34,920 --> 00:25:36,650
who's only living for herself.

520
00:25:37,290 --> 00:25:39,450
I wish you could see my sister's face.

521
00:25:39,840 --> 00:25:41,910
S-She was completely stunned.

522
00:25:42,790 --> 00:25:44,510
She went absolutely livid.

523
00:25:46,570 --> 00:25:48,840
But seeing her so angry,

524
00:25:49,790 --> 00:25:51,720
I felt really happy.

525
00:25:53,630 --> 00:25:54,300
Was that...

526
00:25:54,460 --> 00:25:55,630
even right?

527
00:25:58,160 --> 00:25:59,100
Thank you.

528
00:26:02,200 --> 00:26:03,530
You did the right thing.

529
00:26:06,150 --> 00:26:07,120
Trust me.

530
00:26:10,810 --> 00:26:12,530
But are you

531
00:26:12,550 --> 00:26:14,630
genuinely happy now?

532
00:26:22,950 --> 00:26:23,670
Fine.

533
00:26:23,830 --> 00:26:25,110
Let's say

534
00:26:25,160 --> 00:26:26,240
you're genuinely happy now.

535
00:26:26,240 --> 00:26:27,790
You've already said so much.

536
00:26:27,790 --> 00:26:28,790
Why not continue

537
00:26:28,820 --> 00:26:30,970
and pour your heart out to me?

538
00:26:31,790 --> 00:26:33,140
Just think of me as

539
00:26:33,350 --> 00:26:34,240
a canvas,

540
00:26:35,030 --> 00:26:36,690
on which you can doodle as you please.

541
00:26:36,690 --> 00:26:38,660
A canvas can't laugh at you, right?

542
00:26:52,210 --> 00:26:53,010
Right.

543
00:26:54,550 --> 00:26:56,030
A canvas can't laugh at me.

544
00:26:58,840 --> 00:26:59,920
There's actually a painting

545
00:26:59,920 --> 00:27:01,120
I'm longing to paint.

546
00:27:01,390 --> 00:27:02,600
I thought about it

547
00:27:02,790 --> 00:27:03,560
for a long time,

548
00:27:03,560 --> 00:27:04,200
but I-I didn't

549
00:27:04,200 --> 00:27:05,720
know where to begin.

550
00:27:06,790 --> 00:27:09,800
I didn't think I was ready.

551
00:27:10,110 --> 00:27:11,640
I even felt I was not worthy.

552
00:27:12,350 --> 00:27:13,750
There was a moment

553
00:27:14,270 --> 00:27:16,390
when I thought I might be ready.

554
00:27:16,530 --> 00:27:17,590
But then I found out

555
00:27:19,760 --> 00:27:22,220
someone else was drawing
the same painting.

556
00:27:23,310 --> 00:27:25,110
The colors were bright,

557
00:27:25,860 --> 00:27:27,320
and the idea was unique.

558
00:27:31,880 --> 00:27:33,270
That said, every painter's

559
00:27:33,270 --> 00:27:34,960
brushstrokes and emotions

560
00:27:35,650 --> 00:27:36,690
are unique.

561
00:27:37,240 --> 00:27:38,000
Really?

562
00:27:41,170 --> 00:27:43,630
But that's someone else's unfinished work.

563
00:27:44,480 --> 00:27:46,280
I'd hate to disrupt the process.

564
00:27:50,000 --> 00:27:51,660
There are plenty of canvases.

565
00:27:53,020 --> 00:27:56,180
You'll surely find the one
that belongs to you.

566
00:27:56,640 --> 00:27:57,400
Trust me.

567
00:27:59,440 --> 00:28:01,040
Because you deserve better.

568
00:28:01,100 --> 00:28:03,010
♪ Life is full of ♪

569
