Xu Miyu's sister came to see her.

601
00:29:31,170 --> 00:29:33,300
They had an unpleasant conversation.

602
00:29:33,440 --> 00:29:34,270
The food is quite good today.

603
00:29:34,270 --> 00:29:35,400
What happened then?

604
00:29:35,840 --> 00:29:36,940
What could've happened?

605
00:29:36,940 --> 00:29:39,430
Her sister stopped making a scene
when she saw

606
00:29:39,430 --> 00:29:40,630
Xu Miyu was taken away.

607
00:29:40,630 --> 00:29:41,360
Don't worry.

608
00:29:41,380 --> 00:29:42,650
I've notified the security.

609
00:29:42,650 --> 00:29:43,880
They're aware of that woman now.

610
00:29:43,880 --> 00:29:45,170
She'll be put under control

611
00:29:45,170 --> 00:29:46,200
