612
00:29:46,200 --> 00:29:47,110
I'm not asking about that woman,

613
00:29:47,110 --> 00:29:48,840
but the one that was taken away.

614
00:29:50,330 --> 00:29:51,090
Was she okay?

615
00:29:52,110 --> 00:29:53,040
You mean Xu Miyu?

616
00:29:55,270 --> 00:29:57,480
The girls at the reception told me

617
00:29:58,240 --> 00:30:00,160
that her sister got physical with her.

618
00:30:00,160 --> 00:30:02,880
Luckily, Mr. Tan was there to see it.

619
00:30:03,390 --> 00:30:04,790
What did the security do?

620
00:30:04,880 --> 00:30:06,090
There were so many employees in the lobby.

621
00:30:06,090 --> 00:30:07,150
Did no one help her?

622
00:30:07,510 --> 00:30:09,740
All security guards
were assigned to the banquet hall.

623
00:30:09,740 --> 00:30:11,560
And don't you know
those working in the lobby?

624
00:30:11,560 --> 00:30:14,090
They love nothing more than drama.

625
00:30:14,120 --> 00:30:16,080
None of them like Xu Miyu.

626
00:30:16,100 --> 00:30:17,640
They'd love to see her get humiliated.

627
00:30:17,640 --> 00:30:19,170
She should've turned to me.

628
00:30:19,650 --> 00:30:20,570
You?

629
00:30:21,190 --> 00:30:22,510
What gives you the right to meddle

630
00:30:22,510 --> 00:30:23,910
with her family affairs?

631
00:30:24,570 --> 00:30:26,700
Your position as the general manager?

632
00:30:30,400 --> 00:30:31,730
Feng,

633
00:30:31,960 --> 00:30:33,160
Xu Miyu

634
00:30:33,160 --> 00:30:35,440
was busy from morning till night,

635
00:30:35,640 --> 00:30:36,680
