636
00:30:36,680 --> 00:30:38,030
Then she finally got off work.

637
00:30:38,030 --> 00:30:40,830
Isn't it nice
that someone is keeping her company?

638
00:30:45,310 --> 00:30:47,770
How are the preparations
for the talk coming along?

639
00:30:47,770 --> 00:30:49,350
The wiring is all set in the venue.

640
00:30:49,350 --> 00:30:51,100
The cold buffet is getting ready.

641
00:30:51,100 --> 00:30:52,530
As for the guest speaker,

642
00:30:52,620 --> 00:30:55,450
I'll personally bring him
to the banquet hall.

643
00:30:55,480 --> 00:30:57,940
Mr. Ji,
we can't reach the guest speaker now.

644
00:30:57,950 --> 00:30:59,630
Ms. Xu is handling it.

645
00:31:02,640 --> 00:31:04,770
Alright. Stop restraining yourself.

646
00:31:05,750 --> 00:31:07,810
If you're concerned, go check on her.

647
00:31:14,600 --> 00:31:15,980
♪ A flicker of dim light ♪

648
00:31:18,110 --> 00:31:19,750
♪ A bowl of warm soup ♪

649
00:31:20,690 --> 00:31:23,020
[Xu Miyu]

650
00:31:21,970 --> 00:31:23,880
♪ People in the city ♪

651
00:31:24,700 --> 00:31:27,640
♪ Squeezing into the hustle and bustle ♪

652
00:31:29,570 --> 00:31:31,380
♪ The palms of time ♪

653
00:31:30,970 --> 00:31:37,470
[How are you doing?]

654
00:31:33,280 --> 00:31:36,420
♪ Grinding away the simple days ♪

655
00:31:37,030 --> 00:31:39,370
♪ Sprinkling them into this busy world ♪

656
00:31:38,200 --> 00:31:39,480
How are you doing?

657
00:31:40,950 --> 00:31:42,990
♪ To be tasted, bit by bit ♪

658
00:31:45,190 --> 00:31:47,680
♪ Embracing this radiant world ♪

659
00:31:48,260 --> 00:31:51,290
♪ Keeps the heart from fading to grey ♪

660
00:31:51,880 --> 00:31:55,000
♪ Life's joy, sorrow, cold, and warmth ♪

661
00:31:55,730 --> 00:31:57,970
♪ Intertwined within the mundane ♪

662
00:31:59,780 --> 00:32:02,970
♪ Let us bravely gather up ♪

663
00:32:03,640 --> 00:32:07,010
♪ The forgotten past ♪

664
00:32:07,990 --> 00:32:10,260
♪ There may be regrets ♪

665
00:32:11,920 --> 00:32:14,160
♪ There may be loneliness ♪

666
00:32:15,710 --> 00:32:17,940
[How are you doing?]

667
00:32:54,340 --> 00:32:58,040
[East Changzhi Road] [Changzhi Road]

668
00:33:25,660 --> 00:33:33,850
[East Changzhi Road] [Changzhi Road]

669
00:33:41,090 --> 00:33:42,990
No way.
Did he really carry her up to his room?

670
00:33:42,990 --> 00:33:44,800
Yes, bridal style.

671
00:33:45,440 --> 00:33:46,960
I heard from the girls on that floor

672
00:33:46,960 --> 00:33:48,470
