673
00:33:48,470 --> 00:33:49,660
There was no way to wake her up.

674
00:33:49,660 --> 00:33:52,170
Well, what's the nature
of their relationship then?

675
00:33:52,170 --> 00:33:54,430
In the past, when Mr. Tan stayed
on this floor,

676
00:33:54,430 --> 00:33:56,350
