677
00:33:56,380 --> 00:33:57,380
Who knows?

678
00:33:57,440 --> 00:33:59,960
Celebrities are good at
keeping their love lives secret.

679
00:33:59,960 --> 00:34:01,400
Just now when Mr. Tan went into his room,

680
00:34:01,400 --> 00:34:02,640
he hung the "Do Not Disturb" sign

681
00:34:02,640 --> 00:34:03,480
