682
00:34:03,500 --> 00:34:04,700
Juan meant to find an excuse to sneak in

683
00:34:04,700 --> 00:34:07,100
and take a peek,
yet she didn't get a chance.

684
00:34:07,680 --> 00:34:11,340
If Ms. Xu spends the night there,
it means they're a couple, right?

685
00:34:23,929 --> 00:34:25,810
[Camera 01]

686
00:34:28,020 --> 00:34:32,010
[Camera 02]

687
00:34:35,570 --> 00:34:38,739
[Camera 03]

688
