♪ Friends comfort me,
telling me to have a drink ♪

696
00:36:10,020 --> 00:36:13,920
♪ But I’ve already started living
like I’m not myself anymore ♪

697
00:36:17,500 --> 00:36:20,380
♪ I feel reluctant ♪

698
00:36:23,740 --> 00:36:29,590
♪ I feel reluctant to recall
or forget those memories ♪

699
00:36:32,080 --> 00:36:35,310
♪ I feel reluctant ♪

700
00:36:38,690 --> 00:36:44,410
♪ I feel reluctant to grab on to anyone
and I can't breathe ♪

701
00:36:45,590 --> 00:36:48,450
♪ I've been indulging myself ♪

702
00:37:02,980 --> 00:37:06,800
♪ I always say
life is already hard enough ♪

703
00:37:10,600 --> 00:37:14,440
♪ So what else is there worth trying for ♪

704
00:37:17,720 --> 00:37:21,870
♪ Friends comfort me,
telling me to have a drink ♪

705
00:37:25,270 --> 00:37:30,070
♪ But I’ve already started living
like I’m not myself anymore ♪

706
00:37:32,850 --> 00:37:36,960
♪ I feel reluctant ♪

707
00:37:39,630 --> 00:37:46,770
♪ I feel reluctant to forgive you
and there's nothing I can do ♪

708
00:37:48,210 --> 00:37:53,400
♪ I feel reluctant ♪

709
00:37:54,480 --> 00:38:00,270
♪ I feel reluctant to grab on to anyone
and I can't breathe ♪

710
00:38:01,630 --> 00:38:04,010
♪ I've cut myself some slack ♪

711
00:38:31,130 --> 00:38:32,350
[Ji Feng]

712
00:38:32,820 --> 00:38:36,160
[How are you doing?]

713
00:38:36,160 --> 00:38:36,790
[I]

714
00:38:41,240 --> 00:38:41,800
[I]

715
00:38:41,800 --> 00:38:43,350
[How are you doing?]

716
00:38:43,410 --> 00:38:44,520
[Thanks for the good work]
[I'll come for a look]

717
00:39:12,220 --> 00:39:14,230
[Do Not Disturb]

718
00:39:16,320 --> 00:39:19,930
[Do Not Disturb]

719
00:39:21,660 --> 00:39:22,500
[Cleaning Service Needed]

720
00:39:23,110 --> 00:39:24,550
She's coming out.

721
00:39:24,550 --> 00:39:26,470
Why is she alone?

722
00:39:40,550 --> 00:39:41,670
Good morning, everyone.

723
00:39:41,670 --> 00:39:42,480
Good morning.

724
00:39:43,710 --> 00:39:44,310
Ying,

725
00:39:44,330 --> 00:39:45,800
can you give me the guest complaint

726
00:39:45,800 --> 00:39:46,480
register?

727
00:39:46,480 --> 00:39:46,960
Sure.

728
00:39:52,110 --> 00:39:52,630
Lu Xiaoyan,

729
00:39:52,630 --> 00:39:54,490
when will you submit your report?

730
00:39:59,350 --> 00:40:00,320
Good morning, Director Bai.

731
00:40:00,320 --> 00:40:01,920
Good morning, Director Bai.

732
00:40:02,440 --> 00:40:04,510
Ms. Xu, hurry to Mr. Ji's office now.

733
00:40:04,590 --> 00:40:06,190
I'll handle the guest complaints.

734
00:40:06,190 --> 00:40:09,390
It's time you dealt with the complaint
against yourself.

735
00:40:09,440 --> 00:40:09,960
Okay.

736
00:40:11,140 --> 00:40:11,880
Lu Xiaoyan,

737
00:40:12,320 --> 00:40:13,880
finish your report quickly.

738
00:40:13,880 --> 00:40:15,340
I'll read it when I return.

739
00:40:24,110 --> 00:40:26,040
Did you do what the complaint says?

740
00:40:26,220 --> 00:40:28,800
[A group complaint
about Xu Miyu's improper conduct]

741
00:40:28,830 --> 00:40:31,830
[Lu Xiaoyan, Chen Fangjian,
Shi Huanhuan, Wang Deping]

742
00:40:32,920 --> 00:40:33,480
Yes, I did.

743
00:40:33,480 --> 00:40:34,940
Were you drunk last night?

744
00:40:37,240 --> 00:40:37,910
Yes, I was.

745
00:40:37,930 --> 00:40:40,190
Did you spend the night in a guest's room?

746
00:40:40,770 --> 00:40:41,480
Yes, I did.

747
00:40:42,780 --> 00:40:45,380
So this complaint is completely justified.

748
00:40:45,640 --> 00:40:47,850
I was brought back here
after getting drunk.

749
00:40:47,850 --> 00:40:50,780
I didn't break any rules or regulations
of the hotel.

750
00:40:51,050 --> 00:40:52,890
I wonder what negative impact I've caused.

751
00:40:52,890 --> 00:40:53,950
You're in the wrong

752
00:40:54,170 --> 00:40:55,630
because you're a staff member of the hotel

753
00:40:55,630 --> 00:40:57,350
and Mr. Tan is a guest.

754
00:40:58,080 --> 00:40:58,920
As I said,

755
00:40:58,920 --> 00:41:00,440
that happened during my off hours.

756
00:41:00,440 --> 00:41:02,230
Is the hotel trying to dictate who I can

757
00:41:02,230 --> 00:41:03,760
be friends with after work?

758
00:41:03,890 --> 00:41:04,790
Friends?

759
00:41:04,900 --> 00:41:05,570
Xu Miyu,

760
00:41:05,600 --> 00:41:06,770
how capable of you,

761
00:41:06,890 --> 00:41:08,750
for turning a guest into a friend.

762
00:41:09,170 --> 00:41:11,040
Do you know how others think of you?

763
00:41:11,040 --> 00:41:12,360
They can't wait to see you

764
00:41:12,360 --> 00:41:13,960
be dismissed from the hotel.

765
00:41:13,980 --> 00:41:15,490
I'll earn their recognition.

766
00:41:15,490 --> 00:41:16,450
Recognition?

767
00:41:17,480 --> 00:41:20,010
They've sent me
this joint compliant letter.

768
00:41:23,440 --> 00:41:24,640
I'm certainly able to

769
00:41:25,150 --> 00:41:26,070
suppress it

770
00:41:26,590 --> 00:41:28,750
and keep you in your position
against broad objection.

771
00:41:28,750 --> 00:41:30,080
But why should I do that?

772
00:41:30,890 --> 00:41:31,820
Are you worth it?

773
00:41:33,630 --> 00:41:35,060
You can't blame them for seizing

774
00:41:35,060 --> 00:41:36,410
this opportunity to bring you down

775
00:41:36,410 --> 00:41:38,540
since you invited your own trouble
by mixing work and personal affairs.

776
00:41:38,540 --> 00:41:39,730
I mix work and personal affairs?

777
00:41:39,730 --> 00:41:40,920
Then what about you, Mr. Ji?

778
00:41:40,920 --> 00:41:42,430
Is your relationship

779
00:41:42,460 --> 00:41:44,600
with Jiang Zhichun purely professional?

780
00:41:44,600 --> 00:41:45,920
Aren't there personal interests

781
00:41:45,920 --> 00:41:48,250
involved in your collaboration with her?

782
00:41:49,800 --> 00:41:51,600
You have every right to demote me

783
00:41:51,630 --> 00:41:52,570
or to dismiss me,

784
00:41:52,600 --> 00:41:53,410
Mr. Ji.

785
00:41:53,430 --> 00:41:54,590
But I have to say

786
00:41:55,000 --> 00:41:56,560
I did nothing wrong

787
00:41:56,630 --> 00:41:58,680
and I don't need anyone's protection.

788
00:41:58,680 --> 00:41:59,610
What did you say?

789
00:42:02,250 --> 00:42:02,810
Ji Feng.

790
00:42:07,960 --> 00:42:08,840
Mr. Ji,

791
00:42:09,960 --> 00:42:12,490
-you're needed in the meeting room.
-Not now.

792
00:42:12,730 --> 00:42:13,710
Just come with me.

793
00:42:13,710 --> 00:42:15,440
You'll know when you get there.

794
00:42:15,840 --> 00:42:18,150
Ms. Xu, get back to your work.

795
00:42:18,170 --> 00:42:19,170
You're free to go.

796
00:42:20,450 --> 00:42:21,480
Yes, Mr. Xue.

797
00:42:33,150 --> 00:42:34,510
Tan Jizhou wants to see you.
